              <div class="msg">
                <p>Hola!</p>
                <p>Te vienes a cenar al centro? <emoji class="pizza"/></p>
                <time>20:17</time>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="self">
                <div class="avatar"><img src="https://i.imgur.com/HYcn9xO.png" draggable="false"/></div>
              <div class="msg">
                <p>Puff...</p>
